= <span style="color: #f5e324;">**RPT**</span> Party Congress

As the economic crisis worsens, the provisional government has naturally taken the blame in the eyes of many in the population for this crisis. 

Seeking to bring it down, regardless of the threat doing so may pose to the fledgling republic, the <span style="color: #f5e324;">**RPT**</span>'s right-wing has agitated against the government, and seeks to either force Grönblom to turn on us or remove him altogether.

Meanwhile, on the party's left-wing, Minister-President Aspelund has attempted to turn the white-collar unions that he leads against Grönblom, viewing him as a weak leader not enough devoted to support of him and his government and too likely to capitulate to industrialist interests.

