The motion of no confidence against him is narrowly defeated, but only through his support for the industrialist motion, one which emphasizes support for Orthaland-type laissez-faire economics and one that heralds it as the key to the depression, the depression that it caused.

Our relations with the party has worsened, as the rift between us grows. Grönblom may turn against the provisional government in time - rumors are that the <span style="color: #f5e324;">republican</span> ministers are planning to resign.